Your next @target run is on us! We've teamed up with @thatsit to give one winner $1,000 to TARGET!  Pick up your school essentials &  #ThatsitMinis - now available nationwide at #Target! PLUS 5 additional winners will receive a YEAR SUPPLY of our mini fruit bars!
 
How to enter:

Follow @thatsit & @kcstauffer 
Like this photo⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
BONUS: Comment why you love #Thatsit bars
BONUS: Tag your friends (1 tag = 1 entry)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

Open to USA residents only. Giveaway ends Thursday 8/26 at 11:59 pm. Winner will be announced on 8/27. Good luck! #Giveaway #TargetHaul #BacktoSchool #ad
